or hypertension.

00:12:01.701 --> 00:12:02.961
And you may ask:

00:12:03.472 --> 00:12:08.953
Can we use this also to reveal
politicians' emotions?

00:12:08.977 --> 00:12:10.517
(Laughter)

00:12:10.541 --> 00:12:12.395
For example, during a debate.

00:12:13.220 --> 00:12:14.673
Well, the answer is yes.

00:12:15.167 --> 00:12:17.111
Using TV footage,

00:12:17.135 --> 00:12:21.181
we could detect
the politicians' heart rate,

00:12:21.205 --> 00:12:23.251
mood and stress,

00:12:23.275 --> 00:12:26.853
and perhaps in the future,
whether or not they are lying to us.

00:12:27.495 --> 00:12:30.491
We can also use this
in marketing research,